// v1.8+ regression: strict mode + cross-module schema + path-tail
// walking through a `pkg.User` parameter into a field. With v1.8e the
// `lib.User u` parameter type lifts to `Schema("User")`, and v1.4
// path-tail walking resolves `u.name` to `String` via the schema's
// field index. The declared return type `Int` then mismatches.
//
// EXPECTED: exactly 1 `MainReturnTypeMismatch` (expected Int, found
// String) and 0 `UnknownReferenceType`. Pre-v1.8e the body would
// have collapsed to `Any` (because `infer_from_type_node` ignored
// imports), the mismatch check would silently skip on `Any`, and
// strict mode would push a false-positive `UnknownReferenceType`
// because `walk_path` saw `Any` head + tail step → `UnknownStep`.
#strict
#import lib from "./lib.relon"
#main(lib.User u) -> Int
u.name
